target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002470_EMETSELCH<tab>Certes, dans mon élan, il se peut que j'en aie trop fait. Vous avez dû apercevoir çà et là le résultat de mon excès de zèle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002480_EMETSELCH<tab>Weeell, there's no point trying to hide it. Yes.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002480_EMETSELCH<tab>Mais puisque nous en sommes rendus là, autant vous dire la vérité<var 1D /var>: vous touchez du doigt le vœu le plus cher des Asciens.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002490_EMETSELCH<tab>Once the rejoining of worlds is complete, Zodiark will regain His full strength and shatter His prison.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002490_EMETSELCH<tab>Une fois la fusion des mondes accomplie, Zordiarche retrouvera sa puissance originelle, et brisera ses chaînes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002500_EMETSELCH<tab>Then we shall offer up the Source's remaining inhabitants in sacrifice, that we might resurrect our brethren who died to bring Zodiark into existence.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002500_EMETSELCH<tab>Nous lui offrirons alors en sacrifice les vies des habitants du monde primitif, en échange de quoi il nous rendra celles de nos anciens camarades partis en martyrs.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002510_EMETSELCH<tab>But what was it that <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var> came here to do, exactly?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002510_EMETSELCH<tab>Et donc<var 1D /var>? Que viens-tu faire ici chez moi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>We came here to stop you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Contrecarrer tes plans.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A7_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>We came here for the Exarch.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A7_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Récupérer l'exarque.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002520_EMETSELCH<tab>Did you now? One last do-or-die attempt to foil my plans before your mind dissolves into madness?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002520_EMETSELCH<tab>Dépêche-toi alors<var 1D /var>! Tu ne pourras plus me régler mon compte une fois le peu de conscience qu'il te reste évaporé...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002530_EMETSELCH<tab>How very, very...heroic of you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002530_EMETSELCH<tab>Quel héroïsme en tout cas... Bravo...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002540_EMETSELCH<tab>In every single age, there is always <var 1A 02 /var>someone<var 1A 01 /var> who wants to stand up to the evil Ascians.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002540_EMETSELCH<tab>Les détracteurs de notre cause finissent toujours par m'horripiler, peu importe l'époque.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002550_EMETSELCH<tab>Always the same arrogance, the same insistence that the world belongs to them. As if theirs were the only rightful claim, theirs the only existence worthy of preservation!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002550_EMETSELCH<tab>Cette façon de débiter des âneries avec une outrecuidance crasse... “Vous n'avez pas le droit<var 1D /var>! Nous incarnons la justice<var 1D /var>! C'est à nous que le monde appartient<var 1D /var>!”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002560_EMETSELCH<tab>Well, you can't have him. The wisdom that man guards may open up new worlds of possibilities.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002560_EMETSELCH<tab>Bas les pattes<var 1D /var>! Je tiens à conserver la mainmise sur ses con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces. Elles ouvrent des perspectives in<var 16 /var>té<var 16 /var>res<var 16 /var>santes, et je ne dis jamais non à la nouveauté.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002570_EMETSELCH<tab>He has unlocked the secrets of travel across the rift─and through time as well, it would seem. Quite an accomplishment for one of his “incomplete” nature.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002570_EMETSELCH<tab>Qu'il ait réussi à voyager à travers les mondes, voire le temps, est tout bonnement remarquable. Comme quoi, même un être humain inachevé est parfois capable de grandes avancées.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002580_EMETSELCH<tab>I must explore the limits of his capabilities, and harness that power for the Ardor.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002580_EMETSELCH<tab>Je vais m'en donner à cœur joie avec lui. Ce sera un atout sup<var 16 /var>plé<var 16 /var>men<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>re dans notre manche, de quoi accélérer encore la réunification des mondes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002590_EMETSELCH<tab>Even now, after everything, you refuse to see reason.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002590_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous verriez vos têtes... Vous ne comprenez rien à rien, ça saute aux yeux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002600_EMETSELCH<tab>You think it unfair that you are subject to suffering? That your lives will be sacrificed for the ancients?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002600_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous n'en revenez pas qu'on vous traite comme du bétail, hein<var 1D /var>? Vous trouvez cela injuste qu'on vous sacrifie en faveur de nos compatriotes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002610_EMETSELCH<tab>Look at me! I have lived a thousand <var 1A 02 /var>thousand<var 1A 01 /var> of your lives!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002610_EMETSELCH<tab>Dans ce cas, regardez-moi bien<var 1D /var>! Car moi, Emet-Selch, j'ai côtoyé les humains de votre espèce plus longtemps que quiconque<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002620_EMETSELCH<tab>I have broken bread with you, fought with you, grown ill, grown old! Sired children and yes, welcomed death's sweet embrace.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002620_EMETSELCH<tab>Je me suis assis à votre table. J'ai partagé vos luttes, vos peines et vos agonies. J'ai vu naître et s'éteindre plus de vos enfants que je ne saurais en compter.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002630_EMETSELCH<tab>For eons have I measured your worth and found you wanting! Too weak and feeble-minded to serve as stewards of any star!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002630_EMETSELCH<tab>Tant de fois, j'ai eu l'occasion de vous mettre à l'épreuve. Tant de fois, vous m'avez déçu. J'en ai désormais la certitude<var 1D /var>: vous êtes une espèce sotte et médiocre, par<var 16 /var>fai<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment inapte à protéger cette planète<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002640_EMETSELCH<tab>Have your recent spats with Vauthry and his sin eaters taught you nothing?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002640_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous savez de quoi je parle. Lors de votre croisade contre Vauthry et les purgateurs, vous aussi en avez été témoins.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002650_EMETSELCH<tab>Have you not learned that your ignorance and frailty beget only endless misery?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002650_EMETSELCH<tab>De la veulerie des faibles... De la morgue des puissants. De ces vies qui se brisent aussi facilement qu'une brindille, et qui perpétuent une litanie de souffrances<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002660_EMETSELCH<tab>How long do you mean to perpetuate this farce? How much more must I endure your bumbling interference?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002660_EMETSELCH<tab>Entre nous... Combien de temps encore cela va-t-il durer<var 1D /var>? Combien de fois devrai-je m'étrangler de frustration avant que vous ne compreniez<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002670_EMETSELCH<tab>Let us imagine that the laws of reality are again undone, and the world faces true annihilation. Do you honestly believe that half your number would sacrifice themselves to save the other?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002670_EMETSELCH<tab>Imaginez que l'harmonie du monde réunifié soit de nouveau brisée, et que vous soyez à votre tour aux portes de l'apocalypse... Pensez-vous vraiment que vos congénères se lèveraient comme un seul homme, et accepteraient pour moitié de se sacrifier<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002680_EMETSELCH<tab>Of course they wouldn't!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002680_EMETSELCH<tab>Non, bien sûr que non<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002690_EMETSELCH<tab>And if <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var> had witnessed history unfold as <var 1A 02 /var>I<var 1A 01 /var> have, you would reach the <var 1A 02 /var>same<var 1A 01 /var> conclusion!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002690_EMETSELCH<tab>Et ne venez pas me contredire<var 1D /var>! Vous avez suf<var 16 /var>fi<var 16 /var>sam<var 16 /var>ment fait face à la nature de l'Homme pour connaître sa lâcheté<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002700_EMETSELCH<tab>You cannot be entrusted with our legacy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002700_EMETSELCH<tab>... Plutôt mourir que de vous laisser prendre les rênes de ce monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002710_EMETSELCH<tab>I will bring back our brethren. Our friends. Our loved ones. The world belongs to us and us alone.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002710_EMETSELCH<tab>Je les ramènerai tous<var 1D /var>: mes chers compatriotes, mes fidèles compagnons... tous ceux à qui le monde revient de droit.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002720_ALPHINAUD<tab>Emet-Selch!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002720_ALPHINAUD<tab>Attendez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002730_ALPHINAUD<tab>We understand. Truly. But it makes no difference.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002730_ALPHINAUD<tab>Emet-Selch... Au fond, vous défendez la même cause que nous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002740_ALPHINAUD<tab>The ones you love are in the past.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002740_ALPHINAUD<tab>Vous voulez offrir une place dans ce monde à vos anciens alliés et à toutes ces personnes chères à vos yeux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002750_ALPHINAUD<tab>While ours are here in the present.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002750_ALPHINAUD<tab>Eh bien, nous aussi. Sauf que dans notre cas, ces gens sont dans le présent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002760_ALPHINAUD<tab>One day, we too will be ashes and dust, but not today. Our time is not yet finished.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002760_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nous avons au moins cela en commun... Aussi, ce que je vais vous dire ne vous surprendra pas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002770_ALPHINAUD<tab>We share your conviction...and that is why we will not abandon our course.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002770_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nous n'avons aucune intention de partir d'ici. Nous resterons, car tel est notre devoir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002780_EMETSELCH<tab>You think us the same? You think your tattered soul of equal worth to those <var 1A 02 /var>I<var 1A 01 /var> lost?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002780_EMETSELCH<tab>Que les choses soient claires<var 1D /var>: nous n'avons rien en commun. Je suis un être complet, vous êtes des succédanés. Si quelqu'un ici doit survivre, c'est moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002790_EMETSELCH<tab>Then come─<var 1A 02 /var>earn<var 1A 01 /var> your place. Prove yourselves <var 1A 02 /var>worthy<var 1A 01 /var> to inherit this star.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002790_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous avez à y redire<var 1D /var>? Allez-y, prouvez-moi que j'ai tort. Que vous valez mieux que les Asciens. Que vous méritez de nous supplanter.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002800_EMETSELCH<tab>Behold, the coming oblivion. 'Twas the end of our era, and the beginning of our great work.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002800_EMETSELCH<tab>L'avènement du chaos... La fin de notre ère, et le début de notre subsistance.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002810_EMETSELCH<tab>A fitting backdrop...for your final judgment.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002810_EMETSELCH<tab>Quelle meilleure épreuve pour vous que de revivre cet instant charnière<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002820_EMETSELCH<tab>I shall wait within, but do not spend too much time on your preparations. There's no telling how much longer the guest of honor will last.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002820_EMETSELCH<tab>Je vous attendrai au fin fond de l'enfer, en compagnie de votre précieux ami. Ne traînez pas, ou la douleur finira par avoir raison de sa ténacité...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002830_EMETSELCH<tab>Well, well, you prevailed...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002830_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous avez vaincu le Mégatherion<var 1D /var>? Im<var 16 /var>pres<var 16 /var>sionnant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002840_EMETSELCH<tab>Nevertheless!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002840_EMETSELCH<tab>Hélas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002841_ALPHINAUD<tab>(HIT REAX)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002841_ALPHINAUD<tab>Argh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002842_ALISAIE<tab>(HIT REAX)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002842_ALISAIE<tab>Guuh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002850_EMETSELCH<tab>Your performance was underwhelming, and I remain unconvinced of your worthiness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002850_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous êtes tous recalés. Tout bien considéré, vous ne m'arrivez pas à la cheville.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002860_EMETSELCH<tab>Oh, you tower over your misbegotten ilk, no doubt. But should I bring my full strength to bear, well...you would be as leaves in the wind.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002860_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous êtes les borgnes parmi les aveugles, la crème de votre espèce. Et pourtant, regardez avec quelle facilité je vous brise.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002870_EMETSELCH<tab>The gulf between us is a reflection of the disparity between the world as it was...and what it has become.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002870_EMETSELCH<tab>Cet écart de force, c'est toute la différence entre le vrai monde et celui-ci. Maintenant, vous savez.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002880_ALISAIE<tab>Hah!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002880_ALISAIE<tab>Haan<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002890_ALISAIE<tab>(GRUNT)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002890_ALISAIE<tab>Guoh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002900_ALISAIE<tab>Our worlds may not live up to your lofty standards...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002900_ALISAIE<tab>Ce monde n'est peut-être pas aussi parfait que le tien...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002910_ALISAIE<tab>But they are <var 1A 02 /var>our<var 1A 01 /var> worlds! <var 1A 02 /var>Our<var 1A 01 /var> homes! Full of life and love and hope!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002910_ALISAIE<tab>Mais nous y sommes attachés... comme tous ceux qui se sont battus pour y vivre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002920_ALISAIE<tab>And we won't stand by and let you destroy them!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002920_ALISAIE<tab>Navrée... mais si tu le veux, il faudra nous passer sur le corps<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002930_ALISAIE<tab>Ugh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002930_ALISAIE<tab>Uaaah<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002940_ALPHINAUD<tab>Alisaie!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002940_ALPHINAUD<tab>Alisaie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002950_EMETSELCH<tab>You are a mistake.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002950_EMETSELCH<tab>L'heure de vérité a sonné. Pour vous et moi, tout se joue maintenant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002960_EMETSELCH<tab>For we who have known perfection, the shattered Source and these shards are ghastly mockeries of the true world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002960_EMETSELCH<tab>Qui a connu le véritable monde sait que le monde primitif et ses reflets ne sont que de pâles copies ne méritant pas d'exister.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002970_EMETSELCH<tab>The ephemeral lives you exalt are pale imitations, utterly devoid of meaning.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002970_EMETSELCH<tab>Et vous voudriez y vivre<var 1D /var>? Allons, un peu de sérieux. Déjà que vos existences sont courtes et pathétiques...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002980_ALPHINAUD<tab>Belittle us all you like, but we will rise again and again, and give the lie to your insults through word and deed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002980_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu as beau dénier notre droit à la vie, nous continuerons de le défendre jusqu'à notre dernier souffle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002990_ALPHINAUD<tab><var 1A 02 /var>We<var 1A 01 /var> define our worth, not the circumstances of our creation!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_002990_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est la somme de ces combats qui nous définit, c'est elle qui donne de la valeur à notre existence... Et tant pis si notre condition humaine laisse à désirer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003000_EMETSELCH<tab>Hmph, more prattle.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003000_EMETSELCH<tab>Ha<var 1D /var>! De belles paroles...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003010_EMETSELCH<tab>Fool. Who are you? No one. <var 1A 02 /var>Nothing<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003010_EMETSELCH<tab>Qui crois-tu être<var 1D /var>? Tu n'es rien ni personne.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003020_EMETSELCH<tab>Once I have reclaimed my heritage, my first act will be to expunge your stain from history's weave.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003020_EMETSELCH<tab>Nous allons reprendre le monde en main. Écrire une nouvelle page de l'histoire, en faisant table rase de votre parcours dérisoire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003030_EMETSELCH<tab>My world will have no need for heroes.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003030_EMETSELCH<tab>Il n'y a pas de héros. Il n'y en a jamais eu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003040_EMETSELCH<tab>Still fighting the good fight...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003040_EMETSELCH<tab>Hum... <var 08 E905 ((Une vraie chienne galeuse)) ((Un vrai chien galeux)) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003050_YSHTOLA<tab>It is true that all we hold dear is fated to fade away.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003050_YSHTOLA<tab>C'est vrai, notre histoire à nous n'est peut-être pas éternelle. Peut-être qu'un jour, tout le monde nous aura oubliés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003060_YSHTOLA<tab>But that is no reason for us to forsake it!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003060_YSHTOLA<tab>Mais ce n'est pas une raison pour renoncer au présent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003070_URIANGER<tab>To take what steps we may, and thus mark the road for those who would follow.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003070_URIANGER<tab>Il faut aller de l'avant, ne serait-ce que pour vivre toutes ces rencontres qui pavent le chemin d'une vie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003080_URIANGER<tab>To strive for the best of all futures... Be this not also thy purpose!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003080_URIANGER<tab>Tisser un lien avec les générations futures... C'est notre souhait... et le vôtre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003090_EMETSELCH<tab>Do not presume to speak of <var 1A 02 /var>my<var 1A 01 /var> future!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003090_EMETSELCH<tab>Dégénérés que vous êtes, comment osez-vous parler en mon nom<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003100_EMETSELCH<tab>And <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>! Why waste your final moments in futile defiance?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003100_EMETSELCH<tab>Tu ne comprendras donc jamais... Qu'espères-tu accomplir en te débattant de la sorte<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003110_EMETSELCH<tab>Weary wanderer─you've no fight left to fight! No life left to live!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003110_EMETSELCH<tab>Âme perdue... Tu n'as plus de raison de te battre... Plus de raison de vivre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003120_EMETSELCH<tab>Hah hah hah hah hah! You see! The Light will not be denied!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003120_EMETSELCH<tab>Haha<var 1D /var>! La Lumière gronde de nouveau<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003130_EMETSELCH<tab>Surrender to your fate, and let the transformation take you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003130_EMETSELCH<tab>Allez, abandonne-toi à elle<var 1D /var>! Deviens le monstre que tout le monde attend<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003140_EMETSELCH<tab>Rise up in madness and fury! Devour the vermin infesting the land which is rightfully ours!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003140_EMETSELCH<tab>Va, et avale jusqu'au dernier de ces pécheurs, de ces voleurs qui s'ébattent depuis trop longtemps sur une terre qui ne leur appartient pas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003150_THANCRED<tab>Now, Ryne! Now!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003150_THANCRED<tab>Ryne, maintenant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003160_EMETSELCH<tab>Bah!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003160_EMETSELCH<tab>Rah...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003170_THANCRED<tab>Hng!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003170_THANCRED<tab>Gah<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003180_RYNE<tab>Fight it... You have to hold on!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003180_RYNE<tab>Tenez bon... Je vous en prie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003190_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>If you had the strength to take another step, could you do it?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003190_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Réponds-moi franchement. Si tu avais la force de te relever, et de mettre un pied devant l'autre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003200_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Could you save our worlds?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003200_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>... tu penses que tu arriverais à sauver ce monde... et tous les autres<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>You know I could!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Évidemment<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A8_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>What, all by myself?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A8_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Oui, mais pas <var 08 E905 ((toute seule)) ((tout seul)) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003210_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Heh.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003210_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>(soupire)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003220_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Take it. We fight as one!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003220_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Allez... Je t'offre mon âme. Prends-la<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003230_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>This world is not yours to end...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003230_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Ce monde n'a pas dit son dernier mot.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003240_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>This is our future. Our story.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003240_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>L'aventure n'est pas terminée, au contraire... elle ne fait que commencer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003250_EMETSELCH<tab>No... It can't be...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003250_EMETSELCH<tab>Comment est-ce possible<var 1D /var>? Toi<var 1D /var>? Ici...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003260_EMETSELCH<tab>Bah, a trick of the light. You are a broken husk, nothing more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003260_EMETSELCH<tab>Non... Il y a erreur... C'est juste une autre de ces con<var 16 /var>tre<var 16 /var>fa<var 16 /var>çons d'humains<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003270_EMETSELCH<tab>How can you hope to stand against me alone?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003270_EMETSELCH<tab>Une contrefaçon qui aurait mieux fait de ramper au sol comme tous ses alliés<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>We stand together!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Pas tous, non<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003290_EMETSELCH<tab>How did─!? ...I'm surprised you can stand at all.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003290_EMETSELCH<tab>Toi... Comment as-tu fait pour t'échapper<var 1D /var>!? Tu étais à l'article de la mort... C'est insensé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003300_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I could not well leave matters half-finished.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003300_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>La Mort m'a accordé un sursis... Elle a bien voulu que je me traîne jusqu'ici pour aider mes amis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003310_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Let expanse contract, eon become instant!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003310_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Entendez ma prière... Traversez l'espace et le temps... Prêtez-moi votre force ici et maintenant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003320_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Champions from beyond the rift, heed my call!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003320_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Venez à moi, combattants émérites, héros d'une autre époque<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003330_EMETSELCH<tab>Damn you! Damn you all!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003330_EMETSELCH<tab>Misérables vermisseaux... Vous avez tous la tête dure, ma parole<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I challenge you, Emet-Selch.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A9_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Finissons-en, Emet-Selch.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A9_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>It ends this day. One way or another, it ends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A9_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Voyons qui de nous aura le dernier mot<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003340_EMETSELCH<tab>Very well. Let us proceed to your final judgment.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003340_EMETSELCH<tab>Très bien... Puisque tu y tiens, je vais t'accorder une ultime épreuve de force.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003350_EMETSELCH<tab>The victor shall write the tale, and the vanquished become its villain!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003350_EMETSELCH<tab>Le vainqueur aura le privilège d'écrire la suite de l'histoire. Le vaincu verra son nom à jamais frappé du sceau de la dissidence et de la honte. Une juste répartition des rôles, sur la grande scène qu'est cette planète<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003360_EMETSELCH<tab>But come! Let us cast aside titles and pretense, and reveal our true faces to one another!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003360_EMETSELCH<tab>Je suis un Ascien, un être plein et entier. Vous me connaissez sous mon nom d'emprunt “Emet-Selch”.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003370_EMETSELCH<tab>I am Hades! He who shall awaken our brethren from their dark slumber!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003370_EMETSELCH<tab>À présent, voici le véritable moi<var 1D /var>: Hadès<var 1D /var>! Celui qui rendra ce monde à ses véritables maîtres<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003380_EMETSELCH<tab>I...will...not...yield.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003380_EMETSELCH<tab>Non... C'est pas fini<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003390_EMETSELCH<tab>Should I surrender this fight, what will become of it all...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003390_EMETSELCH<tab>Si je ne suis plus là pour les incarner, qui le fera<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003400_EMETSELCH<tab>What will become of our triumphs? Our hopes? Our...our despair?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003400_EMETSELCH<tab>Nos souvenirs... Notre volonté... Nos espoirs... Nos désillusions<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003410_EMETSELCH<tab>What of this anguish which yet burns in my breast even after the passing of eons?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003410_EMETSELCH<tab>Cette douleur qui ne m'a jamais quitté... Ces regrets qu'une éternité n'a pu effacer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003420_EMETSELCH<tab>No, no, no! I will not let it all be for naught!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003420_EMETSELCH<tab>Jamais... Jamais je ne laisserai tout cela disparaître<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003430_THANCRED<tab>Enough, damn you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003430_THANCRED<tab>N'y compte même pas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003440_EMETSELCH<tab>Raaargh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003440_EMETSELCH<tab>Gnuuuuh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003450_YSHTOLA<tab>Such...<var 1A 02 /var>infernal<var 1A 01 /var>...strength...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003450_YSHTOLA<tab>Bonté divine... D'où tire-t-il une telle puissance<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003460_EMETSELCH<tab>Raaaaaargh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003460_EMETSELCH<tab>Wouoooooh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003470_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ugh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003470_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ugh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003480_URIANGER<tab>Now! Strike with all thy might!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003480_URIANGER<tab>Maintenant<var 1D /var>! Portez-lui le coup de grâce<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003490_EMETSELCH<tab>Remember...remember us...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003490_EMETSELCH<tab>... J'ai une dernière faveur à te demander.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003500_EMETSELCH<tab>Remember...that we once lived...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003500_EMETSELCH<tab>Souviens-toi de nous... N'oublie jamais que nous avons existé...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003510_ALPHINAUD<tab>It's over. Emet-Selch is no more!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003510_ALPHINAUD<tab>Cette fois, c'est fini... Je n'en reviens pas, vous avez réussi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003520_ALISAIE<tab>More importantly, how do <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var> fare?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003520_ALISAIE<tab>Tes vertiges de tout à l'heure, ça va mieux<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003530_URIANGER<tab>...What dost thou see?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003530_URIANGER<tab>Il y a un problème<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003540_YSHTOLA<tab>His aether... It is...it is as it used to be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003540_YSHTOLA<tab>Elle est là... Je peux de nouveau la voir... Son aura éthérée d'origine...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003550_YSHTOLA<tab>Her aether... It is...it is as it used to be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003550_YSHTOLA<tab>Elle est là... Je peux de nouveau la voir... Son aura éthérée d'origine...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003560_YSHTOLA<tab>As a disciple of Zodiark, the Ascian was the Darkness to your Light...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003560_YSHTOLA<tab>Tout à l'heure, Emet-Selch a utilisé son pouvoir d'adorateur de Zordiarche, le pouvoir des Ténèbres...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003570_YSHTOLA<tab>I can but assume that when you set your strength against his, the Light within you was spent.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003570_YSHTOLA<tab>Vos énergies se sont entrechoquées à pleine puissance... Est-ce que par hasard... ce serait cet impact qui aurait neutralisé toute la Lumière en toi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003580_RYNE<tab>No. It's more than that.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003580_RYNE<tab>Et encore, s'il n'y avait que ça...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003590_RYNE<tab>Under the strain of that incredible flood of aether, your soul had begun to break apart. Yet now it seems somehow...restored.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003590_RYNE<tab>On pensait que ce déferlement éthéré aurait raison de votre âme. Et pourtant, la voilà intacte... Comme si elle s'était réparée toute seule.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003600_RYNE<tab>I tried to help you before the battle, but Emet-Selch stopped me. So, h-how did you─exactly what did you... Can you tell us what happened?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003600_RYNE<tab>Comment est-ce possible<var 1D /var>? Je n'ai rien pu faire pour vous aider avant le combat... Je ne comprends pas... Il a forcément dû se passer quelque chose entre-temps, mais quoi<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I had help from a hero of this world...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Un héros de ce monde m'a aidé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A10_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'll explain it all another time...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A10_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je vous raconterai un jour...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003610_RYNE<tab>I see...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003610_RYNE<tab>C'est bien mystérieux...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003620_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Where to start...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003620_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ahem... Je, euh... Comment dire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003630_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>I believe I owe you all an apology. And you most especially.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003630_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je m'excuse... de vous avoir menti... à tous... et à toi en particulier...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_Q11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Let's get out of here first!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>C'est oublié. Rentrons à présent<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A11_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'm tired─we'll leave the lecture for later.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A11_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je suis trop fatigué<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> pour vous en vouloir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A11_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>'Tis good to see you awake, G'raha Tia.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_A11_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>G'raha Tia, comme on se retrouve<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003640_THANCRED<tab>No arguments here!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003640_THANCRED<tab>Je n'aurais pas dit mieux<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003645_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>うう
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003645_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>うう

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003650_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Well... 'Tis good to be awake!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003650_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>... N'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>? Tout le plaisir est pour moi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003660_CHAINUZZ<tab>So, those mad souls dove straight into the ocean over there, did they?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003660_CHAINUZZ<tab>Donc, vous les avez vus plonger dans ces eaux-là<var 1D /var>!? Vous êtes sûrrrr<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003670_IRVITHE<tab>Ah, a-all I could see from here was the whale, Master Chai...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003670_IRVITHE<tab>Euh... De qui vous parlez<var 1D /var>? Moi, tout ce que j'ai vu, c'est une baleine géante...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003680_DULIACHAI<tab>'Twas surely Alphinaud and those friends of his! They did something <var 1A 02 /var>heroic<var 1A 01 /var>, mark my words!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003680_DULIACHAI<tab>C'est Alphinaud et ses amis à coup sûr<var 1D /var>! Ces petits bouts de chou ont dû accomplir l'une de ces bonnes actions dont ils ont le secrrret<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003690_DULIACHAI<tab>You need only look up there for proof of that!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003690_DULIACHAI<tab>Ce ciel en est la prrreuve<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003700_CHAINUZZ<tab>As you say, my love.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003700_CHAINUZZ<tab>Oui, tu as forrrcément raison.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003710_CHAINUZZ<tab>They're sure to be back─any moment now. Any moment...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003710_CHAINUZZ<tab>D'ailleurs ils vont revenir très bientôt, je dirrrais même plus... maintenant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003720_DULIACHAI<tab>They are coming back, aren't they? I couldn't bear the thought of...of...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003720_DULIACHAI<tab>On va les revoir, hein<var 1D /var>? Ne me dis pas qu'il leur est arrivé malheurrr, je ne le supporterais pas...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003730_DULIACHAI<tab>(SOBBING)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003730_DULIACHAI<tab>(sanglote)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003740_CHAINUZZ<tab>There, there, dear. Everything will be all right...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003740_CHAINUZZ<tab>Chérie, ne pleure pas... Ça va aller, d'accorrrd<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003750_GRITHIL<tab>There! There! Look, over there! Over at the beach!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003750_GRITHIL<tab>Hé<var 1D /var>! Regardez là-bas, sur la berge<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003760_IRVITHE<tab>Ho there!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003760_IRVITHE<tab>Ohééé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003770_GRITHIL<tab>Greetings!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003770_GRITHIL<tab>Par ici<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003780_CHAINUZZ<tab>You all right!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003780_CHAINUZZ<tab>Ça vaaa<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003790_DULIACHAI<tab>Welcome baaack!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003790_DULIACHAI<tab>C'est bon de vous revoirrr<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003800_ALPHINAUD<tab>I didn't think...we'd be swimming...the <var 1A 02 /var>whole<var 1A 01 /var> way back...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003800_ALPHINAUD<tab>Je n'en reviens pas... qu'on ait dû revenir à la nage...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003810_ALPHINAUD<tab>Heavens...heavens... Take me...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003810_ALPHINAUD<tab>Je suis... à bout... de forces...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003820_ALISAIE<tab>Alphinaud!? Oh, hells...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003820_ALISAIE<tab>Hé<var 1D /var>! Alphinaud, ça va<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003830_RYNE<tab>Wait! Where's Urianger!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003830_RYNE<tab>Les amis, c'est terrible<var 1D /var>! Urianger a disparu<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003840_THANCRED<tab>He must have fallen behind...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003840_THANCRED<tab>Mais quand est-ce qu'il nous a faussé compagnie, lui...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003850_RYNE<tab>But...shouldn't we look for him!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003850_RYNE<tab>J-je vais partir à sa recherche tout de suite<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003860_YSHTOLA<tab>He'll wash up sooner or later.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003860_YSHTOLA<tab>Non, laisse-le... Je suis sûre qu'il va nous rattraper.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003870_ALISAIE<tab>For the love of─ Alphinaud!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003870_ALISAIE<tab>Allez, Alphinaud, on se réveille<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003880_FEOUL<tab>Welcome back, dear ones!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003880_FEOUL<tab>Bon retour sur la terre ferme, tout le monde<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And thus did salvation come to the First.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003890_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Et c'est ainsi que le premier reflet fut sauvé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003900_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>The lamps of Amaurot will fade along with Emet-Selch's enchantments, and the depths shall be as once they were.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003900_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>La magie d'Emet-Selch dissipée, les lumières d'Amaurote s'éteindront, et la fosse sous-marine retrouvera son obscurité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003910_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mt. Gulg will one day fall, and the Talos below yield to wind and rain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003910_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Le Mont Gulg retombera sur terre bien assez tôt. Le vent et la pluie se chargeront de rendre le talos géant à Mère Nature.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003920_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>This tale, too, will fade with time, passing into legend as the world heals and moves on.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003920_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Avec le temps, ce monde pansera ses blessures. Et le récit de cette aventure ne sera plus qu'un lointain mythe...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003930_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nevertheless...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003930_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Cependant...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003940_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>As aether obeys the cycle─as death and decay gives way to new life...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003940_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>L'énergie éthérée rendue à la mer des étoiles reviendra un jour irriguer cette terre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003950_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>So too do the memories we share inspire others to rise to greatness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003950_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Votre histoire et celle de ce héros ne manqueront pas de faire des émules.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003960_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>For we who walk before may lead those who walk after.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003960_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ils viendront à leur tour en aide à d'autres personnes, forgeant une chaîne solidaire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003970_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Your road goes ever on, as does your story. As does your legacy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003970_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Ainsi le souvenir de ton périple, et de ceux qui nous ont cédé leur place dans ce monde, vivra éter<var 16 /var>nel<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003980_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Such is the hero's lot─to touch the lives of countless others...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003980_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Préservé dans nos mémoires... et dans celle du héros qui te succédera...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003990_NEXTHEROBOY<tab>Excuse me! You're the Warrior of Darkness...aren't you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_003990_NEXTHEROBOY<tab>P-pardon, <var 08 E905 ((M'dame)) ((M'sieur)) /var><var 1D /var>! Vous êtes <var 08 E905 ((la Guerrière)) ((le Guerrier)) /var> des Ténèbres, pas vrai<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004000_NEXTHEROBOY<tab>Where are you from, really? And how did you get to be so strong!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004000_NEXTHEROBOY<tab>Dites, dites<var 1D /var>! D'où est-ce que vous venez<var 1D /var>? Comment vous avez fait pour devenir aussi fort<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004010_NEXTHEROBOY<tab>Where are you from, really? And how did you get to be so strong!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004010_NEXTHEROBOY<tab>Dites, dites<var 1D /var>! D'où est-ce que vous venez<var 1D /var>? Comment vous avez fait pour devenir aussi forte<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004020_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>By your deeds has the blinding Light been banished from these skies, and the sin eaters driven to retreat.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004020_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Toutes mes félicitations. Grâce à vous, le premier reflet est enfin libéré de la menace des purgateurs, ainsi que du manteau lumineux qui recouvrait ses terres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004030_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Although our many hurts will be years in the mending, I have faith that this world and her people will one day be whole once more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004030_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Tout n'est pas encore revenu à la normale... mais disons que ce monde est bien parti pour s'embellir de jour en jour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004040_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>With no Rejoining in prospect, the Source need no longer fear the coming of an Eighth Umbral Calamity.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004040_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Nous avons en tout cas empêché sa disparition, et prévenu un huitième fléau dans le monde primitif par la même occasion.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004050_YSHTOLA<tab>And with that triumph, the future from which you came will no longer come to pass... Yet, here you still stand.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004050_YSHTOLA<tab>J'en déduis aussi que le futur d'où vous venez n'est plus relié à ce présent. J'avais un peu peur des con<var 16 /var>sé<var 16 /var>quen<var 16 /var>ces, mais... vous êtes toujours là.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004060_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>...So I do. I wonder if that other age continues onward somehow, cut adrift from time's flow? Or have I simply etched myself a place upon this new block of history?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004060_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Bien observé<var 1D /var>! À cela, je vois deux ex<var 16 /var>pli<var 16 /var>ca<var 16 /var>tions possibles<var 1D /var>: soit mon futur continue d'exister indépendamment, soit j'ai définitivement migré vers cet espace-temps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004070_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Either way, this is an unexpected development.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004070_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>À vrai dire, ce n'est pas vraiment ça qui m'inquiète...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004080_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>As the summoner of your souls, my death was meant to release you back to your world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004080_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Étant à l'origine du sort qui vous a amenés ici, mon sacrifice aurait dû permettre le renvoi de vos âmes dans le monde primitif.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004090_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Yet I am very much alive, and you are still stuck here in the First.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004090_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mais vu qu'il n'a finalement pas eu lieu... vous vous retrouvez coincés avec moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004100_ALPHINAUD<tab>I believe I speak for us all when I say that we are happy to postpone our return if it means your life is spared. We will seek out another way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004100_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est assez fâcheux, en effet... mais rien ne nous empêche de chercher un autre moyen de rentrer chez nous. Un procédé qui n'implique aucun sacrifice, cette fois...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004110_ALISAIE<tab>Besides, I never had any intention of rushing home. There are people here I still need to thank, and this means I might actually have time to do so.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004110_ALISAIE<tab>De toute façon, on ne comptait pas repartir tout de suite. Il faut encore qu'on rende visite à tous ceux qui nous ont aidés durant notre séjour. Quelque part, ça tombe plutôt bien.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004120_URIANGER<tab>Yet we dare not neglect our comrades in the Source.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004120_URIANGER<tab>Certes... mais tâchons tout de même de ne pas délaisser nos amis et nos proches du monde primitif trop longtemps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004130_URIANGER<tab>Mistress Tataru, to name but one, will be most anxious to know how things stand with us.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004130_URIANGER<tab>Je pense notamment à ma<var 16 /var>de<var 16 /var>moi<var 16 /var>sel<var 16 /var>le Tataru. Notre trésorière doit compter les jours qui la séparent de notre retour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004140_THANCRED<tab>So─you'll just have to make the journey alone for the moment. Be sure and give a full report to our fellow Scions, would you? Oh, and we'd also appreciate any news you can bring us from back home.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004140_THANCRED<tab>Hé, pourquoi vous ne feriez pas l'aller-retour<var 1D /var>? Comme ça, vous pourriez à la fois raconter nos aventures à toute la bande et nous rapporter des nouvelles du front. D'une pierre deux coups<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004150_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Then I see no reason to delay. I can open the path from here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004150_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je peux t'y expédier tout de suite si c'est ce que tu veux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004160_YSHTOLA<tab>I imagine we each have matters demanding our attention, so let this be a farewell for us all.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004160_YSHTOLA<tab>Vu que chacun a l'air d'avoir ses propres affaires à régler, je propose qu'on en reste là pour cette fois.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004170_YSHTOLA<tab>Send word when you've resummoned our friend.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004170_YSHTOLA<tab>Faites-nous savoir quand notre ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> sera de retour, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004180_YSHTOLA<tab>Oh, and do try to ensure <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> arrives <var 1A 02 /var>within<var 1A 01 /var> the city next time.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004180_YSHTOLA<tab>Et vous serez gentil de ne pas <var 08 E905 ((la)) ((le)) /var> faire atterrir au milieu de nulle part, cette fois-ci...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004190_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Hah! Of course! I shall strive for utmost accuracy! No strange forests or unplanned passengers, I promise.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004190_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Pas d'erreur de destination... ni de passagers en plus<var 1D /var>! C'est promis<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004200_RYNE<tab>I'm a little relieved, to be honest. I would have been terribly lonely if everyone had suddenly disappeared...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004200_RYNE<tab>Ah, je respire... J'aurais été bien triste de devoir vous faire des adieux précipités.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004210_RYNE<tab>But I understand that you have to go. Safe journey, Warrior of Darkness. I hope to see you again soon!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004210_RYNE<tab>Il ne me reste plus qu'à attendre patiemment votre retour... Profitez bien de votre voyage<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004220_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Just a moment while I attune the portal, then you can be on your way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004220_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Bien, je vais mettre la machine en route.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004230_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>When I was a boy, many long years ago...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004230_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Il m'arrive parfois de repenser à ma tendre enfance...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004240_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>...I yearned to stand tall as the heroes of eld.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004240_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je me passionnais pour ces héros qui peuplent les livres et les chansons.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004250_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>But like a fool seeking to pluck the stars from the heavens, my every attempt to reprise their deeds fell short...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004250_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>C'était comme s'ils vivaient dans un autre monde, hors d'atteinte. Je pouvais les imiter, mais ça n'allait pas plus loin.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004260_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>And then, one day, an all but forgotten dream from my youth stood before me, in the flesh.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004260_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Je ne me doutais pas qu'un beau jour, l'incarnation de tous mes rêves apparaîtrait sous mes yeux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004270_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>A hero who looked to the horizon and beyond, and saw I knew not what.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004270_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Mon <var 08 E905 ((héroïne)) ((héros)) /var>... Je me demande ce que l'avenir lui réserve.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>All I knew was that I would give anything to stand at that hero's side.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004280_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Et plus encore, si je pourrai un jour arpenter ce chemin à ses côtés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004290_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Would that it were so easy...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004290_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Évidemment, tout n'est pas si simple...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004300_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>The glory of the heavens was ever beyond the grasp of those who never thought to reach for it. But if I've gained anything from all of this, it is the courage to stretch out my hand.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004300_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Bah, l'espoir fait vivre. Sans compter que je suis bien plus hardi qu'avant. J'ai appris des meilleurs, héhé...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004310_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Do you hear me, G'raha Tia? This is no time for sleeping!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004310_MYSTERYVOICE<tab>Allez, G'raha Tia, du nerf... Ce n'est plus le moment de rêvasser.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004320_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Meanwhile, in the imperial palace in the Source...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004320_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Pendant ce temps, au palais impérial de Garlemald

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004330_ESTINIEN<tab>Hmph.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004330_ESTINIEN<tab>Encore des cadavres...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004340_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>To the west gate! I want to know what's happening there.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004340_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Foncez jusqu'à la porte ouest<var 1D /var>! Je veux un état des lieux au plus vite<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004350_ESTINIEN<tab>Same as the others─struck down with a single blow. An unfortunate day to draw guard duty.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004350_ESTINIEN<tab>Eux aussi... tués d'un coup d'épée net et précis. Décidément, il ne fait pas bon monter la garde à Garlemald.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004360_ESTINIEN<tab>Forgive me. These were your people.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004360_ESTINIEN<tab>... Mauvaise blague, désolé. Apatride ou pas, tes sentiments sont toujours les mêmes...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004370_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>We took advantage of this slaughter to slip into the palace. 'Tis not for me to grieve them.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004370_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Peu importe... Ce serait hypocrite de pleurer leur mort alors que j'ai profité de leur malchance pour infiltrer le palais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004380_VARIS<tab>(-???-)Aaagh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004380_VARIS<tab>(-???-)Uguah<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004390_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>That was the Emperor!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004390_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Ce cri... c'était l'Empereur<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004400_ESTINIEN<tab>Wha─ Wait!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004400_ESTINIEN<tab>Hé, attends<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004410_ESTINIEN<tab>(GRUNT)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004410_ESTINIEN<tab>Ahhh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004420_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Your Radiance!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004420_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Votre Excellence<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004430_ZENOS<tab>(-???-)Gaius! You've missed your part in this, I'm afraid.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004430_ZENOS<tab>(-???-)Ce cher Gaius. Tu arrives après la bataille, je le crains.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004440_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Identify yourself, demon!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004440_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Toi... Tu vas commencer par me dire qui tu es<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004450_ZENOS<tab>You were hoping for the Ascian?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004450_ZENOS<tab>(-???-)J'aurais aimé te répondre “un Ascien”... mais ce serait mentir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004460_ZENOS<tab>The craven shed this skin and fled rather than face me. A pity─I was looking forward to crossing blades with myself.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004460_ZENOS<tab>Cet imposteur a décampé, juste après s'être débarrassé de mon enveloppe physique. Alors que je me faisais une joie de m'affronter moi-même... Tant pis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004470_ZENOS<tab>But I cannot deny the feeling of satisfaction...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004470_ZENOS<tab>Enfin, je dois avouer que ce bon vieux corps commençait à me manquer...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004480_ZENOS<tab>Body and soul, reunited at last!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004480_ZENOS<tab>Cette fois, ça y est<var 1D /var>: Zenos yae Galvus est enfin redevenu lui-même<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004490_ESTINIEN<tab>What now? The game continues, but the pieces have changed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004490_ESTINIEN<tab>Qu'est-ce qu'on fait maintenant<var 1D /var>? Avec un adversaire pareil, la partie risque de grandement se corser.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004500_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Only if we trust in a paragon's words─a mistake I do not intend to repeat.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004500_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Viens là, serpent... Ma lame saura si tu dis la vérité<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004510_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>(CRY)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004510_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Huooooooh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004520_VARIS<tab>Gaius!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004520_VARIS<tab>Attends<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004530_VARIS<tab>He speaks...the truth...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004530_VARIS<tab>Tout ce qu'il dit... est vrai...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004540_VARIS<tab>Elidibus is gone... Tore a hole into the rift...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004540_VARIS<tab>L'Ascien qui contrôlait son corps... Elidibus... Il s'est enfui... en déchirant les cieux...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004550_VARIS<tab>(GRUNT)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004550_VARIS<tab>Gurgh...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004560_VARIS<tab>Zenos... My foolish, greedy son...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004560_VARIS<tab>Zenos... Mon fils<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004570_VARIS<tab>Was a second life not enough? Was the Empire too rich a prize to ignore?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004570_VARIS<tab>Non content de revenir d'entre les morts, tu veux t'emparer de ce pays... Ta voracité t'aveugle, tu ne respectes plus aucune règle...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004580_VARIS<tab>True freedom for our nation─our people─will never be won by a spoiled princeling! The burden of this throne is beyond you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004580_VARIS<tab>Petit insolent<var 1D /var>! Tu n'as pas la carrure d'un chef d'État... Jamais tu ne libéreras ce peuple du fardeau de son histoire, de la malédiction qu'il porte dans ses gènes<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004590_ZENOS<tab>Hmph. 'Tis you, Father, who have struggled with this burden. Simply holding the Empire together has occupied your limited faculties.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004590_ZENOS<tab>Ha<var 1D /var>! Moi, vorace<var 1D /var>? C'est plutôt toi qui manques d'ambition. Toi qui n'as fait que maintenir à flot l'empire dont tu as hérité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004600_ZENOS<tab>But you may take comfort in knowing that I have no intention of pursuing your tedious agenda, nor am I interested in ruling over the Empire's lands.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004600_ZENOS<tab>Garde donc tes projets médiocres et ennuyeux, ils n'ont aucun intérêt à mes yeux. Pas plus que n'en a cette nation, d'ailleurs.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004610_ZENOS<tab>I came only to remove that which ruins my sport. I will not have my prey stolen by your petty wars and cowardly weapons.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004610_ZENOS<tab>En revanche, tu as osé t'en prendre à mes proies, avec ta guerre interminable et tes armes de lâche. Je suis donc venu remettre les pendules à l'heure.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004620_VARIS<tab>You would kill me just for that...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004620_VARIS<tab>C'est absurde... une telle hécatombe... juste pour ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004630_ZENOS<tab>I need no other reason. Any and all who interfere with my hunt...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004630_ZENOS<tab>C'est une raison suffisante. Tu as gâché mon plaisir de chasser.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004640_ZENOS<tab>...will not do so twice!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004640_ZENOS<tab>Meurs à présent<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004650_VARIS<tab>(SCREAM)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004650_VARIS<tab>Guaaaaaaaargh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004660_ZENOS<tab>I heard the Ascian speak of Zodiark and Hydaelyn. Even the will of this star is but a construct of our own making...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004660_ZENOS<tab>Ce pathétique Ascien l'a dit<var 1D /var>: Hydaelyn, Zordiarche... En fin de compte, même la volonté de l'astre n'est en réalité qu'une invention des hommes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004670_ZENOS<tab>We shall gorge upon their strength, and then, my friend, our contest shall begin anew.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004670_ZENOS<tab>Dans ce cas, mon ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, il ne nous reste plus qu'à dévorer leur pouvoir... et à nous affronter de plus belle<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004680_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Zenos!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004680_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Crèèève<var 1D /var>!!!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004690_ZENOS<tab>Hmph...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004690_ZENOS<tab>Hmph.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004700_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>...May I?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004700_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Je peux m'asseoir ici<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004710_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>You, I think, are from a time beyond ours. Have you followed in the wake of Emet-Selch?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004710_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Arrête-moi si je me trompe, mais j'ai comme l'impression que tu n'appartiens pas à notre époque... Je suppose que tu es à la recherche d'Emet-Selch.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004720_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Nay, there is no cause for alarm. I am simply a shade. Here and not here.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004720_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)<var 48 F20223 /var>Tu n'as rien à craindre de moi. Je ne suis rien de plus qu'une ombre désincarnée.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004730_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>I know only that my name is Hythlodaeus, and that this city is a recreation─a phantom moment plucked from the well of history.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004730_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Mon nom est Hythlodaeus... Je le sais, tout comme je sais que cette cité n'est qu'une illusion, la reproduction fidèle d'un paradis perdu...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004740_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>These others seem unaware of their pale existence, but I wonder if Emet-Selch's mind was distracted when it came to my reconstitution.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004740_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Les autres ombres ne semblent pas en avoir conscience... À croire qu'Emet-Selch était d'une humeur différente lorsqu'il m'a recréé...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004750_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>A stray thought would have been enough. “Hythlodaeus will realize the truth,” for example. We were...close friends once, you see...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004750_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Peut-être s'est-il dit que moi, son ami de toujours, je finirais de toute façon par percer son illusion.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004760_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Yet in spite of my perception, I play the same role as all the rest─a bit part, meant to bring color and noise to this well-crafted stage. Too much scrutiny, and we shall burst like the fragile bubbles we are.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004760_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Reste que je n'existe que pour égayer l'Amaurote de ses souvenirs. En ce sens, je suis comme tous les autres, aussi impalpable et éphémère que l'écume des vagues...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004770_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Thus I tell you again: my presence is naught to concern you. I wish only to share your company whilst we wait.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004770_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Alors tu vois, tu n'as aucune raison de te méfier. Je veux juste passer quelques instants en ta compagnie.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004780_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>...If you've come this far, then you know of the catastrophe which awaits us on our “morrow.”<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004780_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>... Tu es au courant, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>? Du grand cataclysme qui nous a frappés après ce jour...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004790_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>The Final Days. What began as isolated incidents soon swelled into a world-spanning threat...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004790_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Des terres reculées, le mal s'est étendu à la planète tout entière, sonnant le début de l'apocalypse.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004800_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>The Convocation of Fourteen─well, it was Thirteen at the time─endeavored to create a will for our star. They would repair the fundamental laws of order and halt the spread of destruction.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004800_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Le Concile des Quatorze... ou plutôt des Treize à ce moment-là, décida de créer la volonté de l'astre dans l'espoir de restaurer l'ordre naturel avant qu'il ne soit trop tard.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004810_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>But creation on such a scale required an immense source of power...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004810_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Or, il lui fallait pour cela un pouvoir démesuré...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004820_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Of those of us who still lived, nearly half offered up their lives in the name of salvation.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004820_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Presque la moitié de la population dut ainsi offrir son énergie vitale, autrement dit se sacrifier.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004830_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>And from their sacrifice, Zodiark was born. Just as we had hoped, He reached forth and halted the march of oblivion.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004830_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>C'est à ce prix que Zordiarche vit le jour. Et que grâce à lui, nous fûmes sauvés de l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004840_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>...Yet oh how the star had suffered. So many species lost. The land was blighted, the waters poisoned, and even the wind had ceased to blow.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004840_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hélas, nos terres étaient entre-temps devenues arides, nos eaux souillées, notre air stagnant. Tant d'espèces s'étaient déjà éteintes...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004850_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Once more did our people give of themselves to Zodiark. Another half of our race sacrificed to cleanse the world; to ensure that trees and grasses and myriad tiny lives would sprout and grow and flourish.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004850_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Une fois de plus, la moitié d'entre nous furent contraints de donner leurs vies à Zordiarche, afin de purifier la planète et d'y resemer des germes de vie.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004860_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>The cycle of life had begun anew, and we reconsidered the means by which we might protect it.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004860_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Puis arriva enfin le renouveau tant attendu. Dès lors, l'humanité tourna son regard vers l'avenir, voulant à tout prix se prémunir d'une nouvelle catastrophe.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004870_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>The Convocation decided thus: we would nurture our world until it was bursting with vitality. Then, when the time was right, we would offer some portion of its living energy to Zodiark...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004870_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>La décision du Concile fut la suivante<var 1D /var>: dès que le monde aurait retrouvé assez de sa splendeur d'antan, une partie des vies qu'il abrite serait offerte à Zordiarche.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004880_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>In return, He would restore to us those brethren whose souls had fed His strength, and together we would resume our role as stewards.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004880_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Ce faisant, nos anciens compatriotes dormant en lui sous forme d'énergie seraient réincarnés.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004890_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>There were, however, those who disagreed with this plan. They argued that enough had been sacrificed to Zodiark─that this new world should belong to the lives newly born.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004890_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Mais des voix dissidentes s'élevèrent bientôt, clamant que les sacrifices devaient cesser, et que les clefs du monde de demain devaient revenir aux jeunes générations.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004900_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>These dissidents surrendered their life energies in the creation of Hydaelyn, an incarnation of their opposing belief. And for the first time in history, our people stood divided... Know you, then, how this conflict ended?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004900_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Ceux-là consommèrent leur énergie vitale pour créer la grande rivale de Zordiarche, Hydaelyn. Pour la première fois de son histoire, l'humanité était divisée en deux camps se livrant une guerre sans merci... Sais-tu ce qu'il advint par la suite<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004910_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>...Hm, I thought you might.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004910_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>... Je me doutais que tu en aurais entendu parler.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004920_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Emet-Selch has ever been a champion for the will of Zodiark.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004920_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Aujourd'hui encore, Emet-Selch continue semble-t-il d'agir au nom de Zordiarche.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004930_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>The original plan may have been set back by millennia, but he will have not abandoned his course. He will pay the price for our return by whatever means is necessary.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004930_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Il a dû user d'innombrables détours entre-temps, mais il nourrit cer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment le même espoir qu'avant, à savoir ressusciter nos anciens compatriotes... en échange d'autres vies.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004940_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>And though he may carry himself with a certain glib ease, Emet-Selch is not a man to bear his burdens lightly. In fact, I imagine they have only grown heavier with every passing century...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004940_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Sous ses airs désinvoltes se cache un homme de passion. Je le connais assez bien pour savoir qu'il ne se déchargerait de son fardeau pour rien au monde.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004950_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>...'Tis truly a terrible weight he has chosen to carry.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004950_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Quel rôle ingrat, vraiment...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004960_AMAUROTADMINISTRATOR<tab><var 48 F20223 /var><var 29 EB02 /var>...<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004960_AMAUROTADMINISTRATOR<tab><var 48 F20223 /var><var 08 E905 ((Madame)) ((Monsieur)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004970_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>It seems your turn has come. Pray do not let me keep you.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004970_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Vas-y, c'est ton tour.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004980_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>...Ah, there was one last thing. You walk with another at your side, yes?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004980_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>... Ah, une dernière chose. Là, juste à côté de toi... il y a une autre personne, je me trompe<var 1D /var>?<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004990_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Nay, I see no definite form...just the faintest suggestion of a second soul. I doubt it visible to anyone but me.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_004990_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Je ne la vois pas, mais je perçois comme une infime présence... Sans doute une autre de mes aptitudes uniques.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005000_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Otherwise, I assume only <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var> can see and hear this ethereal companion?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005000_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>J'imagine que tu es <var 08 E905 ((la seule)) ((le seul)) /var> à pouvoir interagir avec elle.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005010_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hm hm hm... Your connection is hardly a coincidence. In our time, the two of you were one─the color of your souls tells the tale.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005010_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Héhé... C'est logique, vos deux âmes partagent une même couleur. Et je sais de qui vous l'avez héritée...<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005020_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>A hue that distinctive cannot be mistaken, no matter how thin the soul is spread.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005020_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Même brisée en plusieurs morceaux, son âme reste reconnaissable entre mille.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005030_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hah! This is just the kind of fate I might expect for one such as he. Surely Emet-Selch has recognized the hint of “him” in you...?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005030_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Ton destin fait écho au sien... D'ailleurs, ça ne m'étonnerait pas qu'Emet-Selch ait fait le rapprochement, sachant l'affection qu'il avait pour lui.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005040_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Hah! This is just the kind of fate I might expect for one such as she. Surely Emet-Selch has recognized the hint of “her” in you...?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005040_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Ton destin fait écho au sien... D'ailleurs, ça ne m'étonnerait pas qu'Emet-Selch ait fait le rapprochement, sachant l'affection qu'il avait pour elle.<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005050_AMAUROTADMINISTRATOR<tab><var 48 F20223 /var><var 29 EB02 /var>...?<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005050_AMAUROTADMINISTRATOR<tab><var 48 F20223 /var><var 08 E905 ((Madame)) ((Monsieur)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var><var 1D /var>!<var 48 01 /var>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005060_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Fare you well, my new old friend. May you find what it is you seek.<var 48 01 /var>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05005_005060_HYTHLODAEUS<tab><var 48 F20223 /var>Bonne continuation à toi, <var 08 E905 ((ma)) ((mon)) /var> pas si nouvel<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>...<var 48 01 /var>
